   BODY-WRAP _ My sister and I have this holiday tradition. Each
year we inevitably find ourselves side by side in our parents'
bedroom, next to the mirrored closet, comparing the size, shape and
relative attractiveness of our butts. (Don't worry _ we're fully
clothed.) (Sturrock, Palm Beach Post). 35. WITH PHOTOS. MOVED.
</P>
