a look at how our eating habits changed and the food products that
came with those changes, century by century. (Parham, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   GET-FRESH _ These foods, wonderful in their essence, also work
well in creative dishes. Whip up a dish with the Sunshine State
stamp on it. Our signature fruits _ the citrus family _ are in
their glory now. Cut them up, juice them, or leave them whole in a
lovely dessert that features spun caramel threads. (Norris, Palm
Beach Post). 60. WITH RECIPES and PHOTOS. MOVED
