   JOEMURRAY-COLUMN _ (Editor's note: Joe Murray was unable to
write his regular column for today. He is recovering from last
weekend. Instead, he submitted his notes, which are reprinted in
their entirety.) (Murray, Cox News Service) MOVED TUESDAY.
