<P>
   EMURRAY-COLUMN _ LUFKIN, Texas _ Tired of seeing Dan Quayle used
as a punching bag just because when he opens his mouth, he sticks
his foot in it? Here are some quotes sent to me via e-mail that
shows when it comes to making stupid statements, athletes can hold
their own with politicians any day. (E. Murray, Lufkin Daily News)
MOVED.
