<P>
   OPIC _ ATLANTA _ The Overseas Private Investment Council is
targeting Latin America for U.S. investment deals, despite recent
economic turmoil in the region. George Munoz, president and chief
executive officer of the federal agency, was in Atlanta last week
to assess local interest in a regional conference the agency is
planning for later this year to promote Latin American investment.
