<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-12 21:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4420 &Cx1f; tta-z
u p BC-NH-VOICES-ART-2TAKES &LR;      01-12 0868
