<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-12 22:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4520 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-ENCRYPTION-EXPORTS-NY     01-12 1167
